{"tid":2146860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人心態好似我咁懶到一個極點？","createTime":"2020-08-09T00:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T22:42:49.000Z","uid":94266,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2383191e0372f0356d98c81ac85e5ecf31326514","tid":2146860,"uid":94266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T00:28:24.000Z","msg":"廢人警告。呢篇野只係表達我既心態有少少同條咸魚冇乜分別既地步。<br />\n<br />\n淨係鍾意攤起到，乜都唔做，唔想郁，就算知到攤起到好無意義都好，都繼續，最勤力就係上吓網咁，咁樣過一日。<br />\n<br />\n家務唔做就緊架啦（去到不能再忍先會做吓）。以前細個，我都以為我淨係procrastinate喺家務，做功課，同溫習呢啲野上面。但呢幾年，我意識到我已經去到，模型懶砌，game懶玩，劇集都拖住唔睇，呢個地步。覺得做呢啲娛樂野好晒精神，就好似做功課咁。就連食野都開始覺得麻煩，因為又要落街買，買完又要煮，煮完又要洗，之後食完又要屙，又要刷牙。就算落街食都係一樣，因為都係要落街。<br />\n<br />\n所以我都好佩服溝女結婚生仔既人，又要畀心機，畀時間，畀錢。到結婚生仔，更加要畀晒成份人工出黎，有經濟壓力。買啲心頭好，又要過屋企海關。其實咁辛苦為乜？我開始明白到之前訪問過嗰位無家可歸者既心態，同點解欣宜減肥之後都變返肥。底線係只要自己養得起自己，夠生活，就冇人可以鬧你。"},{"pid":"2c1ad2eaa30da3acd4b73e4927449fc4449e7506","tid":2146860,"uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T00:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好正"},{"pid":"5b6e266ba28c26b9033215227e0dbffb482d9bd3","tid":2146860,"uid":176797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T00:32:19.000Z","msg":"Same"},{"pid":"5e2351beb91fd92a0439c39963f51ac91c730a47","tid":2146860,"uid":120987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:13:38.000Z","msg":"咁飛機打唔打？"},{"pid":"58ef419476fd4298fbe4b50c054c6cf65dbf997c","tid":2146860,"uid":94266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e2351beb91fd92a0439c39963f51ac91c730a47","tid":2146860,"uid":120987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:13:38.000Z","msg":"咁飛機打唔打？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"打，咸濕呢啲天性黎。"},{"pid":"321d206cdc87f70027f5ab4b57c9f796bce6e679","tid":2146860,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"一樣。"},{"pid":"4983f50a7cdf9db2f87af9ab621a0bf0d9df7c19","tid":2146860,"uid":99700,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"有時我懶到灘係張床度急尿都懶得去 唔係急到忍唔到都唔會去"},{"pid":"ede1257e81f4d608da7649701d568c9c10d28043","tid":2146860,"uid":309148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:35:35.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係人生<br />\n做到隻狗咁其實都係想要呢啲嘢<br />\n不過好的時候第一次做到隻狗之後之後繼續做到隻狗咁直到死為止"},{"pid":"5f1d17b5f93fb7a43cb01023817bb5c34bb238ee","tid":2146860,"uid":1188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"一樣 咁勤力唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8a3d689ad2f0f78b1cdd4b25eabdbbd5c46bbf","tid":2146860,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"變老...."},{"pid":"8666612ba2ed261cedbab1e429d1470fdc86a5a9","tid":2146860,"uid":28702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:38:02.000Z","msg":"我放假都係咁，寧願訓落張床度上網都唔想做任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d7a5745477525df47b82505b30e47eab5535d5","tid":2146860,"uid":10014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"樓主有無返工？"},{"pid":"a947e49df0e9cdadde840c9dd42bbe037aba030e","tid":2146860,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:39:01.000Z","msg":"想郁咪郁<br />\n唔想郁咪唔撚郁囉<br />\n呢d先係自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8355256b90f2046f5f6b894a9f6a5e0de6d3f5c7","tid":2146860,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52d168ca20f2fcb1535b2bbb50f614b37ff179ba","tid":2146860,"uid":317378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:42:32.000Z","msg":"廢柴表示認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac5ea577896033be4a4353e716fd15b146d341d","tid":2146860,"uid":22104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy